<h2 id="heading">@</h2>
<p>You can use this shortcode to create a link to a GitHub user or Twitter user. For example, 

<a href="https://github.com/gohugoio">@Hugo</a> and 

<a href="https://twitter.com/gohugoio">@GoHugo.io</a>.</p>
<p>Here is the code:</p>





<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-text" data-lang="text"><span class="line"><span class="ln">1</span><span class="cl">{{&lt; at name=Hugo type=github id=gohugoio &gt;}}
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="ln">2</span><span class="cl">{{&lt; at name=&#34;GoHugo.io&#34; type=twitter id=gohugoio &gt;}}</span></span></code></pre></div>]]></content:encoded></item></channel></rss>